\n*: Western Bukidnon Manobo: {{tt|mbb|saɣing}}\n* Manx: {{tt|gv|bananey}}, {{tt|gv|corran bwee}}\n* Māori: {{tt+|mi|panana}}, {{tt|mi|maika}}\n* Maranao: {{tt|mrw|saging}}\n* Marathi: {{tt|mr|केळे}}\n* Masbatenyo: {{tt|msb|saging}}\n* Melanau:\n*: Central Melanau: {{tt|mel|baleak}}\n* Mohawk: {{t|moh|teiotahià꞉kton}}, {{t|moh|baná꞉ne}} {{q|dated}}\n* Mon: {{tt|mnw|ဗြာတ်|tr=brāt}}\n* Mongolian:\n*: Cyrillic: {{tt+|mn|гадил}} {{qualifier|official}}, {{tt+|mn|банан}}, {{tt|mn|банана}} {{qualifier|popular}}\n*: Mongolian script: {{tt|mn|ᠭᠠᠳᠠᠯᠢ}}, {{tt|mn|ᠪᠠᠨᠠᠨ}}, {{tt|mn|ᠪᠠᠨᠠᠨᠠ}}\n* Motu: {{tt|meu|bigu}}\n* Muong: {{tt|mtq|chuổi}}\n* Murut:\n*: Tagal Murut: {{tt|mvv|punti}}\n* Navajo: {{tt|nv|hashkʼaan}}\n* Nepali: {{tt+|ne|केरा}}\n* Norman: {{tt|nrf|banane|f}} {{qualifier|Jersey}}\n* Norwegian:\n*: Bokmål: {{tt+|nb|banan|m}}\n* Nupe: {{tt|nup|yàbà}}\n* Occitan: {{tt+|oc|banana|f}}\n* Odia: {{tt+|or|କଦଳୀ}}\n* Ojibwe: {{tt|oj|akandamoo}}\n* Oromo: {{tt|om|muuzii}}\n* Paiwan: {{tt|pwn|veljevelj}}\n* Palawano:\n*: Brooke's Point Palawano: {{tt|plw|punti}}\n* Pangasinan: {{tt|pag|pontí}}, {{tt|pag|punti}}\n* Pannonian Rusyn: {{t|rsk|банана|f}}\n* Pashto: {{tt|ps|کيله|f|tr=kila}}\n* Persian:\n*: Dari: {{tt|prs|کیلَه}}, {{tt+|prs|موز}}\n*: Iranian Persian: {{tt|fa-ira|مُوْز}}, {{tt|fa-ira|بَنان}} {{qualifier|rare}}\n* Pipil: {{tt|ppl|kinia}}\n* Plautdietsch: {{tt|pdt|Banan|f}}, {{tt|pdt|Boomworscht|f}}\n* Polish: {{tt+|pl|banan|m}}\n* Portuguese: {{tt+|pt|banana|f}}\n* Punjabi:\n*: Gurmukhi: {{tt+|pa|ਕੇਲਾ|m}}\n* Puyuma: {{tt|pyu|belrbelr}}\n* Quechua: {{tt|qu|latanu}}, {{t|qu|latanus}}\n* Rapa Nui: {{tt|rap|māika}}\n* Rohingya: {{tt|rhg|kelā}}\n* Romagnol: {{tt|rgn|banâna|f}}\n* Romanian: {{tt+|ro|banană|f}}\n* Romansh: {{tt|rm|banana|f}}\n* Rukai: {{tt|dru|belebele}}\n* Russian: {{tt+|ru|бана́н|m}}\n* Saaroa: {{tt|sxr|tavʉhlʉvʉhlʉ}}\n* Saisiyat: {{tt|xsy|tawmo'}}\n* Sakizaya: {{tt|szy|paza'}}\n* Sambali: {{tt|xsb|batag}}\n* Samoan: {{tt|sm|fa'i}}\n* Sangil: {{tt|snl|vusa}}\